data.description: Tucked down a long private drive you will find this wonderful, 2,863 sq ft, 4 Bedroom home, sited on a peaceful 5 acre lot. This well designed home features a grand entry with soaring ceilings on the main floor, dining room, den/office space, and an open kitchen layout. Upstairs you will find the spacious primary suite with dual closets and 5 piece bath. 3 additional bedrooms are also upstairs supported by two full bathrooms for added convenience. New roof, furnace, and heat pump all within the last year. Flat and useable 5 acre property with a good mix of trees and open space! Large deck off the rear of the home is great for entertaining! 3 car garage & 2 outbuildings for additional storage. 10 min to I-5. Call today to schedule a tour!
